        <item>
            <title>美研可穿戴血压计大小如邮票，非入侵技术超声波随时量血压</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/05/researchers-develop-wearable-patch-that-monitors-blood-pressure-anywhere/life-tech/health/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=researchers-develop-wearable-patch-that-monitors-blood-pressure-anywhere</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/05/researchers-develop-wearable-patch-that-monitors-blood-pressure-anywhere/life-tech/health/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 10:00:17 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[健康]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[美国研究]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[血压计]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[超声波]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1279421</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>美国研究团队宣布成功开发一款超声波贴片，能以非入侵性方式持续监测人体血压。目前相关研究论文已刊登在权威科学期刊《Nature（自然）》，贴片已收集逾百名患者临床测试数据，有望为心血管健康监测带来新突破。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279423" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/wearableultrasoundpa-1-694x363.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="363" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/wearableultrasoundpa-1-694x363.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/wearableultrasoundpa-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://scitechdaily.com/researchers-develop-wearable-patch-that-monitors-blood-pressure-anywhere/">Sci Tech Daily</a></p><p>美国加州大学圣地牙哥分校（(University of California San Diego，UC San Diego）在权威学术期刊《Nature》发表研究论文，表示成功开发一款超声波贴片，具有柔软且可拉伸的特性，能以非入侵性方式持续监测人体血压。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279430" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024120531933-694x564.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="564" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024120531933-694x564.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024120531933.jpg 1107w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="text-align: center; font-size: 16px;">▲岛桥结构使贴片具有柔软且可拉伸的特性<br />
图片来源：</span><a style="text-align: center; font-size: 16px;" href="https://today.ucsd.edu/story/wearable_ultrasound_patch_monitors_blood_pressure_deep_inside_body">UC San Diego</a></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279426" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/saizhouholdingultras-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/saizhouholdingultras-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/saizhouholdingultras.jpg 777w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲UC San Diego 研发团队成员之一，图片来源：<a href="https://scitechdaily.com/researchers-develop-wearable-patch-that-monitors-blood-pressure-anywhere/">Sci Tech Daily</a></p><p>这款贴片大小与邮票相若，使用方式亦与邮票相近，用家可以将贴片贴在前臂，能够实时提供精确的深层组织血压读数。贴片矽胶弹性体制成，使用小型电压感测器发送和接收超声波，以追踪血管直径的变化，进而转换为血压数值。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279427" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/wearableultrasoundpa-2-694x363.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="363" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/wearableultrasoundpa-2-694x363.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/wearableultrasoundpa-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://scitechdaily.com/researchers-develop-wearable-patch-that-monitors-blood-pressure-anywhere/">Sci Tech Daily</a></p><p>传统袖带式血压计每次只可提供单次血压值，无法纪录血压详细波动资讯，而 SC San Diego 最新研发的贴片可量度连续的血压波形数据，纪录血压波动的详细趋势。据外媒报道，贴片在临床测试的表现与传统袖带式血压计和动脉导管相当。动脉导管数据虽然精准，但需要刺穿患者皮肤，具有侵入性，量度时可能引起不适，并限制患者的活动，反观贴片则无须刺穿患者皮肤，同时亦不会限制患者活动，另外亦可长时间测量患者血压变化。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279433" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/maxresdefault-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/maxresdefault-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/maxresdefault-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲传统袖带式血压计，图片来源：<a href="https://i.ytimg.com/vi/M_LpuQJxm3A/maxresdefault.jpg">YouTube</a></p><p>UC San Diego 研究人员收集了 117 名参与测试病患的数据，包括在日常活动和不同姿势下的血压监测，结果证实了贴片的安全性比动脉导管更高，而且准确性与传统量度血压方式（袖带式血压计、动脉导管）非常一致，技术有望提升临床和家庭环境心血管健康监测精准度，为患者和医护人员提供更便捷的血压监测工具。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279424" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/bloodpressurepatchon-694x254.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="254" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/bloodpressurepatchon-694x254.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/bloodpressurepatchon.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://today.ucsd.edu/story/wearable_ultrasound_patch_monitors_blood_pressure_deep_inside_body">UC San Diego</a></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://scitechdaily.com/researchers-develop-wearable-patch-that-monitors-blood-pressure-anywhere/">Sci Tech Daily</a>、<a href="https://today.ucsd.edu/story/wearable_ultrasound_patch_monitors_blood_pressure_deep_inside_body">UC San Diego</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
