            <title>杨润雄免职后 FB 发文，「天空海阔，踏上人生另一阶段」，</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/05/kevin-yeung/life-tech/social-network/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=kevin-yeung</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/05/kevin-yeung/life-tech/social-network/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 05:24:08 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[城中热话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[社交网络]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1279387</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>今日（5 日）上午，杨润雄被中华人民共和国国务院免去文化体育及旅游局局长职务。稍早前杨润雄在个人 Facebook 发文感谢各方关心，表示「天空海阔，踏上人生另一阶段。」下面有网民留言指：「希望你真系退休，唔好再去下一个岗位再拖累香港人」。</p><p><iframe loading="lazy" style="border: none; overflow: hidden;" src="https://www.facebook.com/plugins/post.php?href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkevinyhyeung%2Fposts%2Fpfbid0YHLoUzPd9VhNq4KmtCpqMr17egEsjQzL4vZYBNi3EsWoV5oEVThukykfuhR1S84el&amp;show_text=true&amp;width=500" width="500" height="230" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279391" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241205_12_26_34-694x477.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="477" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241205_12_26_34-694x477.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241205_12_26_34.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/share/p/1Yiss6NgER/">Kevin Yeung@Facebook</a></p><p>另外有网民回应，笑指杨润雄被免职一事可用作教训小朋友不要迟交功课。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279395" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241205_12_44_42-694x97.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="97" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241205_12_44_42-694x97.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/20241205_12_44_42.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/share/p/1Yiss6NgER/">Kevin Yeung@Facebook</a></p><p>据《香港电台》报道，国务院决定根据行政长官李家超的提名和建议，免去杨润雄的文化体育及旅游局（文体局）局长职务，罗淑佩将会接任文化体育及旅游局局长一职。</p><p>杨润雄在任期间曾发生多宗事件引起社会关注，去年香港开始步出疫情阴霾逐渐复常，旅游业盼举办更多盛事吸引游客。2024 年 2 月美职联球队国际迈阿密访港，原定球星美斯会上场与港队进行表演赛，惟最终美斯并未落场与港队进行表演赛，事后杨润雄指主办方有责任向球迷交代。</p><p>行政长官李家超公布今年《施政报告》后，曾点名批评文体旅局未有如期公布《文艺创意产业发展蓝图》更提及局方不可推卸责任。被行政长官点名批评之后一日，杨润雄在记者会被多次追问如何回应被特首点名。杨润雄回应指不觉得李家超有多次公开催促他。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1782181-20241205.htm">RTHK</a>、<a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1782193-20241205.htm">RTHK</a>、<a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1782183-20241205.htm">RTHK</a>、<a href="https://www.facebook.com/share/p/1AcPagPL8K/">Kevin Yeung@Facebook</a>、<a href="https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=1802774516860796">文体局@Facebook</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 倾倾科技背后黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/05/kevin-yeung/life-tech/social-network/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
